    <briefdescription>
<para>API for the application to notify the system of the reason it will exit. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>If the application has not specified an exit reason before it exits, then the exit reason will default to APP_EXIT_NOT_SPECIFIED.</para>
<para>Only an application can set its exit reason. The system will not modify it. </para>
